Here is the pipeline:

Calendar features:
https://www.kaggle.com/pratikkumar/m5-forecasting-calendar-events-minfeats

item, store, sell_price, calendar:
https://www.kaggle.com/pratikkumar/m5-point-forecast-createinput-1100

Weight and scaling factor for each item_store as per the evaluation metric for the competition:
https://www.kaggle.com/pratikkumar/m5-point-forecast-valweights

Weight and scaling factor for each aggregtion group as per the evaluation metric:
https://www.kaggle.com/pratikkumar/m5-pointforecast-agggroups-idxs-k-val

Target_lag, Target_lag_rolling feature, model input ordering for efficient evaluation of custom objective:
https://www.kaggle.com/pratikkumar/m5-pointforecast-itstorder-hist-val

LGBM Training with custom objective based on the evaluation metric
https://www.kaggle.com/pratikkumar/m5-pointforecast-modeltrain-customobj-val-final/data?scriptVersionId=37776771
